Package com.ericbarnhill.jvcl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Boundaries
    This class finishes boundaries for Unrolled and GPU methods.
    FDCPU
    This class performs naive Finite-Differences convolutions on the CPU.
    FDGPU
    This class performs Finite-Differences convolutions on the GPU.
    FTCPU
    This class performs Fourier-domain convolutions on the CPU.
    JVCLTest  
    JVCLUtils
    This collection of static utility methods contains several methods called by the convolution classes, and several methods that may be convenient for the convolution calls of users.
    Unrolled
    This class provides unrolled methods for many common convolutions.
    Unroller
    This class generates code for unrolled convolutions.
